TELC:sample.name: EXTENDED_TELE_ID_SPECIFIC_HEADER
TELC:sample.TELC:description: NOT a counter. Indicates the format of extended fixed telemetry regionBits 7:0 - NUM_RAW_BLOCK_REASONS - Number of counters in "raw block reasons" sub-categoryBits 15:8 - NUM_RAW_WAKE_REASONS_PC6_PC10Bits 23:16 - NUM_DEMOTION_CAUSES_PC6_PC10Bits 31:24 - NUM_BLOCK_CAUSES_PC6_PC10

TELC:sample.name: PACKAGE_CSTATE_WAKE_REFCNT
